 * This will make all future AJAX requests timeout after a specified amount
 * of time.
 *
 * Set to null or 0 to disable timeouts (default).

 * @cat Ajax
 */
ajaxTimeout: function( timeout ) {
	jQuery.ajaxSettings.timeout = timeout;
},
